{
  "text": "Language models enable access to powerful technologies that not only offer suggestions for content (Duval et al. 2021) but can also reformulate poorly written text, translate text from one language to another, generate summaries from long and multiple documents, give feedback on a given piece of written text (Gao 2021), and even construct articles, essays and stories (Cotton et al. 2024).",
